    <p>Profiling &amp; &ldquo;cookie&rdquo; files &ndash; does it affect your rights? Cookies are files that a given website introduces to the User&rsquo;s computer through a web browser (with the User&rsquo;s consent), allowing websites to recognize a given browser in order to acquire and remember selected information about the browsing history. We follow &ldquo;cookies&rdquo; to better understand and remember our users&rsquo; preferences. You can disable &ldquo;cookies&rdquo; tracking in the settings of your web browser. Our services in matters related to data storage and analysis are based on Google solutions.</p>

